  <Content
    isReversed
    tagline=""
    title="<a name='divisio-escalabilitat' title='Break down large systems into more specialized and scalable tools'>Modularization & Scalability</a>"
    subtitle="Sometimes, using a single platform or software to meet multiple requirements is not the best solution."
    items={[
      {
        title: 'Functionality Segmentation',
        description: 'We break down monolithic systems into modular components to improve management and scalability.',
      },
      {
        title: 'More Agile Development',
        description: 'Allows for targeted updates and expansions, reducing time and costs.',
      },
      {
        title: 'Minimized Error Impact',
        description: 'Modular blocks operate independently, reducing the impact of errors on the overall system.',
      },
    ]}
    image={{
      src: '~/assets/images/bloques-distribuidos.png',
      alt: 'Dividing a project into scalable modules',
    }}
  >
    <Fragment slot="preContent">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-3xl mb-2">Transforming Monoliths into Scalable Systems</h3>
      <p class="text-muted">
        Monolithic systems can be challenging to maintain and update. Breaking these systems into modular components
        enables agile development and improved scalability.
      </p>
    </Fragment>
    <Fragment slot="postContent">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-3xl mb-2">Benefits of Modularization & Scaling</h3>
      <p class="text-muted">
        Modular architectures improve manageability and make it easier to introduce new functionalities with minimal
        disruption.
      </p>
    </Fragment>
    <Fragment slot="bg">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-lightgray"></div>
    </Fragment>
  </Content>

  <Features
    id="benefits"
    tagline="Agile and Transparent Implementations for Users"
    title="What Are the Benefits of Performing Migrations and Integrations with Gilsys?"
    subtitle="We execute migrations efficiently and turn integrations into opportunities to evolve systems sustainably, without unnecessary investment."
    items={[
      {
        title: 'Seamless Migration Process',
        description: `We ensure that every migration or integration is carried out with <strong>minimal impact</strong> on daily operations. 
        We meticulously plan and coordinate each stage to maintain business continuity and reduce disruptions for end users.`,
        icon: 'tabler:arrows-horizontal',
      },
      {
        title: 'Honestedat i enfoc personalitzat',
        description:
          'A Gilsys prioritzem les necessitats reals del client. Si no és necessari canviar-ho tot, o no té sentit a nivell econòmic fer-ho, ho exposarem de forma transparent. Recomanem les pràctiques i solucions més adequades per cada projecte, valorant sempre el cost-benefici i l’impacte a llarg termini.',
        icon: 'tabler:message-circle',
      },
      {
        title: 'Experiència pràctica en projectes reals',
        description: `Hem treballat amb empreses de sectors molt diversos, resolent problemes concrets com la integració de sistemes independents, la migració d'eines a aplicacions més modernes o dividint plataformes per convertir-les en més escalables a nivell d'arquitectura i funcional.`,
        icon: 'tabler:chart-bar',
      },
      {
        title: 'Desenvolupament pensat per al futur',
        description:
          'Cada migració i integració es planteja amb una <strong>estratègia a llarg termini</strong>. Dissenyem sistemes flexibles que evolucionen amb l’empresa, permetent afegir noves funcionalitats, integrar eines modernes i adaptar-se als canvis tecnològics sense necessitat de reconstruir des de zero.',
        icon: 'tabler:leaf',
      },
    ]}
  />
  <CallToAction
    backgroundImage={{ src: '~/assets/images/dots/03.jpg', alt: 'Abstract background' }}
    actions={[
      {
        variant: 'primary',
        text: 'Get a Free Quote',
        href: u('contact'),
      },
      {
        variant: 'primary',
        text: 'Call Us',
        href: 'tel:+34665331271',
      },
    ]}
  >
    <Fragment slot="title"
      >Looking to <span class="custom-gradient">migrate</span> legacy tools or <span class="custom-gradient"
        >integrate applications</span
      > into your business?</Fragment
    >
    <Fragment slot="subtitle"
      >Get in touch with us, and we’ll handle the consultation and execution of your project.</Fragment
    >
  </CallToAction>
</Layout>
